# link
https://docs.substrate.io/tutorials/smart-contracts/prepare-your-first-contract/

# install ink-contract

## Stable version
cargo install cargo-contract --version 2.0.0-alpha.3 --locked

## newest version
cargo install --force --locked cargo-contract --version 2.0.1

# test
cargo contract test

# build
cargo contract build


# run node
substrate-contracts-node --log info,runtime::contracts=debug 2>&1

